---
---
<!-- ── COMPARISON ────────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
<section class="py-32 max-md:py-20 bg-bg" id="comparison">
  <div class="layout-wrap">
    <div class="fi mb-16 opacity-0 translate-y-[18px] transition-[opacity,transform] duration-[650ms] ease-out [&.in]:translate-y-0 [&.in]:opacity-100 text-center flex flex-col items-center">
      <div class="mb-3.5 text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-text-kicker before:text-[rgba(139,124,255,0.62)] before:content-['//_']">Why Chain Hub?</div>
      <h2 class="mb-5 font-display text-[clamp(30px,3.5vw,50px)] font-bold leading-[1.02] tracking-[-0.06em]">Stop repeating yourself.<br><em class="not-italic text-accent">Start scaling.</em></h2>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-border overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-border">
      <!-- The Old Way -->
      <div class="fi bg-surface p-10 opacity-0 translate-y-[18px] transition-[opacity,transform] duration-[650ms] ease-out [&.in]:translate-y-0 [&.in]:opacity-100">
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-text-kicker mb-8 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></span>
          The Old Way
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-6 list-none">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-red-400 mt-1">—</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-text mb-1">Manual Copy-Pasting</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-dim leading-relaxed">Repetitively pasting your brand voice or project rules into every new chat window.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-red-400 mt-1">—</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-text mb-1">Inconsistent AI</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-dim leading-relaxed">Claude knows your style, but Gemini is still using generic defaults because you forgot to update its settings.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-red-400 mt-1">—</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-text mb-1">Lost Knowledge</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-dim leading-relaxed">Your best prompts and expert instructions are buried in old chat logs, impossible to find or reuse.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- The Chain Hub Way -->
      <div class="fi bg-surface-2 p-10 opacity-0 translate-y-[18px] transition-[opacity,transform] delay-100 duration-[650ms] ease-out [&.in]:translate-y-0 [&.in]:opacity-100 relative overflow-hidden">
        <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-8 opacity-10 pointer-events-none" aria-hidden="true">
          <svg width="120" height="120" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor"><path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm-1 14H9v-2h2v2zm0-4H9V7h2v5zm4 4h-2v-2h2v2zm0-4h-2V7h2v5z"/></svg>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-accent mb-8 flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="size-2 rounded-full bg-accent animate-pulse"></span>
          The Chain Hub Way
        </h3>
        <ul class="space-y-6 list-none">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-accent mt-1">+</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-text mb-1">Update Once, Smarter Everywhere</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-dim leading-relaxed">Change a guideline in your Hub, and every AI assistant instantly follows the new rule.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-accent mt-1">+</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-text mb-1">Universal Consistency</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-dim leading-relaxed">Your brand voice, expert skills, and project context are identical across all your favorite AI apps.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <span class="text-accent mt-1">+</span>
            <div>
              <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold text-text mb-1">Permanent Library</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-text-dim leading-relaxed">Build a long-term asset of expert knowledge that you own and control, forever.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
